hello! This website is about providing people with high quality notes, in pakistan students of 9th-12th do not want any concept clearance, they just want notes, tricks and paper presentation patterns they can follow easily and score. So, this website wants to solve this issue by giving high quality notes, long questions which have been attempted by hand with presentation and board paper timing tailored towards students of pakistan. Such websites do not exist, they do for other countries but not for Pakistan. Here students can just come to get a list of top questions in a chapter, the easy to follow mnemonics for short questions, and other essential info which is usually locked behind the paywall of an institution fee. This website provides all the high quality study and cramming material to students who live in far off places or cannot afford high fees. This is completely free of cost and no ads shall be run here. Also i do not want to sell anything to anyone so i dont need to have a front page that "sells" or "converts" users, so do not do it. It should be a beautiful, minimal , decluttered website that doesnt shout at the users about how good this site is, it just gives the material in dedicated sub sections

